article.description: — Justin Vander Baan had 16 points in Lafayette's 59-51 victory against Boston University on Saturday.
article.headline: Vander Baan scores 16, Lafayette beats Boston University 59-51
article.linkText: Vander Baan scores 16, Lafayette beats Boston University 59-51
article.story: BOSTON -- — Justin Vander Baan had 16 points in Lafayette's 59-51 victory against Boston University on Saturday. Vander Baan added nine rebounds, three steals, and four blocks for the Leopards (3-12, 2-0 Patriot League). Kyle Jenkins shot 7 for 11, including 0 for 3 from beyond the arc to add 14 points. Eric Sondberg shot 2 for 5 (1 for 3 from 3-point range) and 3 of 4 from the free throw line to finish with eight points. Nic Nobili led the Terriers (5-10, 0-2) in scoring, finishing with 13 points and three steals. Otto Landrum added 12 points for Boston University. Ethan Okwuosa also had nine points and seven rebounds. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
